[Solid justification in 2–4 sentences: what fired (`rule` + behavioral pattern), the specific benign evidence, and why no durable filter is safe — name the anchor/boundary problem (only volatile identifiers distinguish it / a viable filter would suppress TPs / would break on cmdline variation / same-host recurrence is the likely TP). CORR history stated.]
